---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<Base
    title="Contact Kids Disease"
    description="How to reach the Kids Disease team for corrections, source suggestions, or content requests. For medical emergencies, always call your local emergency number."
>
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Contact Us' }]} />

    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-8 space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-[#F1EDFF] tracking-tight">Contact Us</h1>

        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-red-200/70 dark:border-red-400/30 bg-red-50/60 dark:bg-red-500/10 p-6 space-y-2">
            <h2 class="text-sm font-black text-red-900 dark:text-[#FFB3A8]">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-truck-medical mr-1.5" aria-hidden="true"></i> Medical emergency?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-red-950 dark:text-[#FFD9D2] font-bold leading-relaxed">
                Do not use this contact channel. Call your local emergency number or go to the
                nearest emergency department immediately.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-night-card rounded-3xl border border-orange-100 dark:border-night-line shadow-premium p-6 md:p-8 space-y-5 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-[#D8D2F5] font-medium leading-relaxed">
            <p>We welcome three kinds of messages:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-xs md:text-sm">
                <li><strong>Corrections</strong> — if any profile conflicts with current AAP/CDC/WHO/NHS guidance, tell us and include the source.</li>
                <li><strong>Coverage requests</strong> — conditions you looked for and didn't find.</li>
                <li><strong>Accessibility issues</strong> — anything that doesn't work with your screen reader, keyboard, or device.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm">
                Open an issue on the project repository:
                <a
                    href="https://github.com/Kangaeruhito14/PediaCare---Premium-Child-Disease-Encyclopedia/issues"
                    rel="noopener"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="text-brand-teal hover:underline font-black"
                >
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-github mr-1" aria-hidden="true"></i>GitHub Issues
                </a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-[#8B84B8] font-bold">
                We cannot answer individual medical questions about your child — that would be
                practicing medicine without an examination, which would be unsafe.
            </p>
        </div>
    </article>
</Base>
